{"tid":1620221,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"大家要聽話，香港建國的機會只有這一次，不要糟蹋了。","createTime":"2019-10-04T09:45:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T14:49:08.000Z","uid":36086,"like":45,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"1e4992e630d9ebdba87b512e4a746a77579d1bd8","tid":1620221,"uid":36086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:45:56.000Z","msg":"《緊急法》啟動之後，該怎麼反應？我認為這是難得的冷卻機會，令社運鬥爭調整目標。<br />\n<br />\n一、君子不吃眼前虧，不要去大型示威：<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">泛民剛好配合政府，即刻宣布了明日在港島區舉辦反蒙面大遊行。這是捕捉港獨派及其他勇武者的陷阱</span></strong>，除去選舉的競爭者，借刀殺人。雖然是法不責眾，衙差不會全部拘捕示威者，但衙差會根據《禁蒙面法》來拘捕他們的目標群體。<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">你蒙面沒事，不代表其他勇武者及少年、少女沒事，不要害人。</span></strong>更何況，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>政府是不會因為和平示威而改變行為的。</strong></span>和平示威要重新制定口號和策略，才會有效。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n二、早期我已經呼籲各位將勇武行動暫停在少女被射盲眼的一日。但大家沒聽，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">現在十月一日，少年被衙差開槍射中胸口，我們要將勇武行動停在這一刻，避免無謂犧牲</span></span></strong>，雖然我知道很多革命行動都是用潛意識裡面的死亡驅動（death drive；thanatos）來做動力，但<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我們是求生，不是求死。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三、期間，調整示威的口號和行動策略<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">。口號是對準共產黨，行動是對準共產黨在香港。</span></strong>一樣是<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>流水鬥爭術，但和平進行</strong></span>。口號和策略用對了，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">具體的行動，我信任各位義民的智慧。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我會觀察香港的司法覆核的情況和國際反應，隨時給各位做匯報和判斷。"},{"pid":"611b64b9537853fb2a75ae2f129bf30b151f4ba7","tid":1620221,"uid":36086,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:47:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">希望大家聽下國師話，不做無謂犧牲。</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"7eb57cd38f8d24f05c3d6cf4cc4ce787221de71e","tid":1620221,"uid":36086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:47:41.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"d2c23bdb2134ac47be24844b1f75884e84521a02","tid":1620221,"uid":36086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:49:01.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"87e1539314ffb88d1c4d8ad2e1ef8fa4f6aabe8a","tid":1620221,"uid":36086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:50:24.000Z","msg":"推3<br />\n<br />\n如果唔聽就，只好祝大家 武運昌隆。"},{"pid":"79c47462fd0dcc00535f9d24600b7456b867efce","tid":1620221,"uid":46422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:52:55.000Z","msg":"其實同意"},{"pid":"b7a1680d70a140c351178aa17173e7b194d5e988","tid":1620221,"uid":205125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:55:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n全民起義 還政於民<br />\n驅逐共黨 香港獨立</span></span>"},{"pid":"2b6034ed8bb10754c1c8769aa464f87ea3f67577","tid":1620221,"uid":41093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:56:04.000Z","msg":"不分化不割蓆 團結！"},{"pid":"2ccb466665fa6e7e8da019ba74018e0c1badccd7","tid":1620221,"uid":75664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:57:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef1d20e9153ad17bd3a9f607bc1278bc3ef027b","tid":1620221,"uid":34334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:05:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43ee6e297626c65cd4437f8a4e505183de5428d8","tid":1620221,"uid":36086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:41:43.000Z","msg":"唔捨得大家犧牲。"},{"pid":"09d0aa12fcffb8c9df41cb3852913549198f1239","tid":1620221,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:45:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97d404f5971cc696f99f8d5e714563891dc5e972","tid":1620221,"uid":66363,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:54:01.000Z","msg":"其實國師有道理"},{"pid":"3ccb13a3a45e423fd397b86df048189c1c8efc3b","tid":1620221,"uid":63017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:56:27.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命<br />\n香港獨立，唯一出路<br />\n希望大家支持獨立建國"},{"pid":"117f9393935a24e1fc0da1de427498edab46e6de","tid":1620221,"uid":210190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:58:26.000Z","msg":"驅逐共黨 光復香港 <br />\n<br />\n大家越憤怒時要越冷靜去應戰！"},{"pid":"d252697f170926aa2e8bbb907e943f6872d50e17","tid":1620221,"uid":36086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:26:07.000Z","msg":"陳雲：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>所謂引蛇出洞。你不是蛇，就不必出動。</strong></span>政府發揮它在山竹超級颱風都不可用的影響力，今日全港學校和辦公室提早放，店鋪關門，公司提早叫人走，大家得閒在街上在商場，泛民就配合政府去舉動示威集會。這些都是trap-setting（佈置陷阱），而且是毛澤東的「陽謀」的級數。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">各國的經驗證明，反蒙面法沒有效果。香港特首動用英王的王權賦予的《緊急法》來訂立禁止蒙面法，必會遇到司法覆核，過不了幾日，毋須去打它而令它可以發生效用。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"19a6587d14655048809b0d1ca56a53580aa23347","tid":1620221,"uid":261478,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:27:22.000Z","msg":"香港人唔好再係人地個框框入面玩啦<br />\n規矩人地定無可能會贏<br />\n出緊急法佢話抄你家就抄你家<br />\n香港人要跳出框框<br />\n宣佈現政府違法並成立臨時政府<br />\n再立即宣佈香港進入戰爭狀態<br />\n同時以臨時政府名義請求聯合國/美軍出兵<br />\n並承諾香港將承擔所有戰爭開支<br />\n籌備明年1月1日大選<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1619715/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1619715/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1620237/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1620237/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1609431/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1609431/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1620656/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1620656/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"459e89164313d66009369878e38f59bbecba4bfd","tid":1620221,"uid":36086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:33:31.000Z","msg":"認真求推,搞左呢份野等三萬黑警都要接受國際審判<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1617815\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1617815</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dce28071b889d98646a9d06c321664f02eb6144c","tid":1620221,"uid":75072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:34:52.000Z","msg":"搵個根據地建國啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"067175a3b35fbd3219e480cc6c760ce99277f0ec","tid":1620221,"uid":299255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:35:53.000Z","msg":"be water"},{"pid":"ed0a81f6cadaebc75b74d95b2d00415c85aebe3c","tid":1620221,"uid":259544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:37:56.000Z","msg":"同意 唔好送頭 要勇武要大戰唔洗急一日半日"},{"pid":"92445d361c8f499d8faadab84fa784a8564a8517","tid":1620221,"uid":63119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:39:30.000Z","msg":"和理非就遊行，衝衝子就各區遊擊，就係咁簡單"},{"pid":"06d5d3f746c07960e470ad30133d62bfdf1a8f19","tid":1620221,"uid":294182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:41:34.000Z","msg":"行街遊行&hellip;罷買中資+賣港+藍屍商店食肆&hellip;持久戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7638f13b3f4547f70d6ff2d7a7924e5588782d11","tid":1620221,"uid":148817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:47:45.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"8ffc0d862be8d86d49785f1d8c24bfe2811c51b7","tid":1620221,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:48:19.000Z","msg":"推"}]}